M' = M + epsilon , M : Original SDF , Epsilon : ESG

Epsilon Component가 Priced 되는 Component인가? 

Pastor, Stambaugh Taylor 의 Effect가 Industry Effect를 Adjust 했는가?

Ex-ante / Ex-post 를 헷갈린 것인가?

Greenium 은 Cash Flow News Driven? Discount Rate News Driven?

Tetlock Paper (Journal of Finance) 2020 에서처럼 Green Factor를 어떤 News Driven인지 

Campbell Shiller Variance Decomposition을 해볼 수 있을 것 같음. 

